    <title>gitee 实现自动部署</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/08/09/gitee-auto/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/08/09/gitee-auto/</id>
    <published>2019-08-09T14:56:31.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-08-09T15:15:09.107Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>github 在国外，之前那个自动部署，是可以用，但是经常超时，然后需要自己登到服务器上去<code>git pull</code></p><p>在网上找了很多 gitee 的自动部署方法，抱歉参考的到底是哪个已经找不到了，就把我自己的流程记下来方便以后使用</p><hr><ol><li><p>自己家的本地库与远程仓库建立联系</p></li><li><p>添加 webhook.php 文件到本地库，且推送到远程仓库</p></li></ol><p>webhook.php 代码：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 本地仓库路径</span></span><br><span class="line">$local = <span class="string">'/www/wwwroot/pull.xasmartliving.com'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 安全验证字符串，为空则不验证</span></span><br><span class="line">$token = <span class="string">''</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 如果启用验证，并且验证失败，返回错误</span></span><br><span class="line">$httpToken = <span class="keyword">isset</span>($_SERVER[<span class="string">'HTTP_X_GITLAB_TOKEN'</span>]) ? $_SERVER[<span class="string">'HTTP_X_GITLAB_TOKEN'</span>] : <span class="string">''</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> ($token &amp;&amp; $httpToken != $token) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    header(<span class="string">'HTTP/1.1 403 Permission Denied'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">'Permission denied.'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 如果仓库目录不存在，返回错误</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!is_dir($local)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    header(<span class="string">'HTTP/1.1 500 Internal Server Error'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">'Local directory is missing'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//如果请求体内容为空，返回错误</span></span><br><span class="line">$payload = file_get_contents(<span class="string">'php://input'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!$payload) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    header(<span class="string">'HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">'HTTP HEADER or POST is missing.'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> *第一次 git clone 后</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 服务器需要修改权限</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * chown -R www .</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * chmod -R g+s .</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> shell_exec(<span class="string">"cd &#123;$local&#125; &amp;&amp; git pull 2&gt;&amp;1"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">"done "</span> . date(<span class="string">'Y-m-d H:i:s'</span>, time()));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li><p>远程仓库添加 webhook<br><img src="http://www.xasmartliving.cn/fujingqi/giteewebhook.jpg" alt></p></li><li><p>登录服务器 git clone 并修改权限</p></li></ol><p><code>git clone https://gitee.com/fujingqi/pull.git pull.xasmartliving.com</code></p><p><code>cd pull.xasmartliving.com</code><br><code>chown -R www .</code><br><code>chmod -R g+s .</code></p><h3 id="done"><a href="#done" class="headerlink" title="done"></a>done</h3>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;github 在国外，之前那个自动部署，是可以用，但是经常超时，然后需要自己登到服务器上去&lt;code&gt;git pull&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在网上找了很多 gitee 的自动部署方法，抱歉参考的到底是哪个已经找不到了，就把我自己的流程记下来方便以后使用&lt;/p&gt;
